1151
00:41:24,235 --> 00:41:25,385
Can't you just let bygones be bygones?

1152
00:41:25,385 --> 00:41:26,345
Why must you interfere?

1153
00:41:26,345 --> 00:41:27,115
Why must you come here?

1154
00:41:27,115 --> 00:41:28,305
