a despicable deed.

1156
00:41:30,945 --> 00:41:31,825
How could you walk tall like this

1157
00:41:31,825 --> 00:41:32,715
when you're the one in the wrong here?

1158
00:41:32,865 --> 00:41:33,785
Are you even a human?

1159
00:41:34,785 --> 00:41:35,595
